summary: SWOT refers to a strategic planning method used to identify strengths, weaknesses, opportunities, and threats related to personal growth, startups, and strategic networking. This concept is fundamental in aligning goals, discovering personal strengths, and fostering self-awareness.
excerpt: Aligning the Misaligned involves a journey of growth and strategic planning. Discovering personal strengths builds confidence and direction. Embracing weaknesses fosters resilience and self-awareness.
